author: scottbw
msg: Added support for supplying a "default identifier" when parsing a widget package. This is important for the Widget Updates feature (see WOOKIE-103), as the updated widget may not contain an identifier element, or may have one that differs from the original for some reason, however we need to ensure the correct folders are written to with the new content.
